text: Fritz Fivian (January 15, 1930 - April 2, 2009) was an American wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman welterweight at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2009 deaths Category:American male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of the United States Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Thun
